ÆIN LOVING MEMORY OF
MARY FRANCES DONNELLY
1912- 1989

MARY DEAR COME HOLD MY HAND
WE'LL WANDER THROUGH THE FLOWERS
WHERE IN THE PAST WE HAD SUCH FUN
AND MANY HAPPY HOURS
PAT."±
ÆIn memory of Fletcher Kendrick Ivimey
stillborn on 24 August 2010
son of Jenny and James Ivimey. Little brother of Sylvie and twin of Lucas
What will survive of us is love"¥
±Gerald Stanford MBE
1937 - 2019
Here sat our friend Gerald, while waiting for the bus.
Sometimes it was late but he never made a fuss.
Cobham Conservation and Heritage Trust"ø
